Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:02.96,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:07.62,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是宇宙大爆炸后产生宇宙时就存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.54,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,古往今来的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:15.40,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,从多数卡片中选择了40枚组合起来构筑了属于自己的卡组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.79,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,进行了激烈的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.45,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.64,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来站在战争历史巅峰造极的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.29,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这究极的最强的卡片游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.29,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「战斗生物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.35,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,美国大选也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.11,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,人气偶像解散也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:33.52,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 动画软件的出货量也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.80,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是由这个「战斗生物」的胜负来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.01,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:41.93,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,得「战斗生物」者得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:45.59,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 全国的「战斗生物」者们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.30,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在拿起卡组站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:52.67,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 投入卡片战争的汹涌海涛之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.15,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:11.61,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.55,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.17,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,超人气卡片游戏 「战斗生物」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:18.20,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,通称「战生」的新卡包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:21.70,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,Evolution of Nerd的开包仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.91,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 先打开第一包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.43,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有稀有卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.82,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且生物全是香草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.24,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个作为开头很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.39,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.15,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟有没有稀有卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.89,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦… 没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.49,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.06,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为没那么容易出才是稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.54,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…没有…没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.18,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是最后一包了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.13,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:25.43,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能看到那动画的禁放集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.32,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能小看重播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.40,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.77,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 是这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.72,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么彻底地全部踩雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.20,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定是被卡片的女神抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.60,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.60,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这个还没开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.21,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.07,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术卡 30年的家里蹲！
