Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:03.16,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正如其名很少见的传说级UR卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.18,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.87,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,保好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.88,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,保有成为「战斗生物」者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.81,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗者的命运力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:14.85,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这种隐藏的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.53,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,保
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.10,akiba-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事是 战斗…
